  "title": "Wellness Coach (Healthcare)",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>Plan, promote, and implement wellness programs and activities at the community centres.</li>\n  <li>Conduct screenings, physical assessments, and track patient progress with follow-ups.</li>\n  <li>Monitor patient participation and compliance with individualized care plans.</li>\n  <li>Maintain and disinfect program equipment regularly.</li>\n  <li>Collaborate with clinical teams to support patient engagement and wellness outcomes.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Requirements:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Diploma in Health Sciences (Health Management), Sports Science, or equivalent.</li>\n  <li>At least 2 years of experience in <strong>healthcare, community care, or wellness program facilitation.</strong></li>\n  <li>Passionate about community service with a proactive and organized approach.</li>\n  <li>Strong interpersonal and communication skills.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>If you are keen to apply for the position, kindly email your detailed resume in<strong> MS Word </strong>to <strong>hr@recruit-expert.com</strong></p>\n<p>Please note that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p>\n<p>For more job opportunities, please visit our website at<a href=\"http://www.recruit-expert.com/\"><strong>www.recruit-expert.com</strong></a></p>\n<p>EA Licence: 19C9701</p>\n<p>Registration: R21100996</p>",
